{"an3.183-352:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 3 ","an3.183-352:0.2":"18. Ragapeyyala ","an3.183-352:0.3":"~ ","an3.183-352:1.1":"“Ragassa, bhikkhave, abhinnaya tayo dhamma bhavetabba. ","an3.183-352:1.2":"Katame tayo? ","an3.183-352:1.3":"Sunnato samadhi, animitto samadhi, appanihito samadhi—","an3.183-352:1.4":"ragassa, bhikkhave, abhinnaya ime tayo dhamma bhavetabba. (…) ","an3.183-352:2.1":"Ragassa, bhikkhave, parinnaya …pe… ","an3.183-352:2.2":"parikkhayaya … ","an3.183-352:2.3":"pahanaya … ","an3.183-352:2.4":"khayaya … ","an3.183-352:2.5":"vayaya … ","an3.183-352:2.6":"viragaya … ","an3.183-352:2.7":"nirodhaya … ","an3.183-352:2.8":"cagaya … ","an3.183-352:2.9":"patinissaggaya ime tayo dhamma bhavetabba. ","an3.183-352:3.1":"Dosassa … ","an3.183-352:3.2":"mohassa … ","an3.183-352:3.3":"kodhassa … ","an3.183-352:3.4":"upanahassa … ","an3.183-352:3.5":"makkhassa … ","an3.183-352:3.6":"palasassa … ","an3.183-352:3.7":"issaya … ","an3.183-352:3.8":"macchariyassa … ","an3.183-352:3.9":"mayaya … ","an3.183-352:3.10":"satheyyassa … ","an3.183-352:3.11":"thambhassa … ","an3.183-352:3.12":"sarambhassa … ","an3.183-352:3.13":"manassa … ","an3.183-352:3.14":"atimanassa … ","an3.183-352:3.15":"madassa … ","an3.183-352:3.16":"pamadassa … ","an3.183-352:3.17":"abhinnaya … ","an3.183-352:3.18":"parinnaya … ","an3.183-352:3.19":"parikkhayaya … ","an3.183-352:3.20":"pahanaya … ","an3.183-352:3.21":"khayaya … ","an3.183-352:3.22":"vayaya … ","an3.183-352:3.23":"viragaya … ","an3.183-352:3.24":"nirodhaya … ","an3.183-352:3.25":"cagaya … ","an3.183-352:3.26":"patinissaggaya ime tayo dhamma bhavetabba”ti. ","an3.183-352:4.1":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","an3.183-352:4.2":"Attamana te bhikkhu bhagavato bhasitam abhinandunti. ","an3.183-352:4.3":"Ragapeyyalam nitthitam. ","an3.183-352:5.0":"Tassuddanam ","an3.183-352:5.1":"Ragam dosanca mohanca, ","an3.183-352:5.2":"kodhupanahapancamam; ","an3.183-352:5.3":"Makkhapalasaissa ca, ","an3.183-352:5.4":"maccharimayasatheyya. ","an3.183-352:6.1":"Thambha